@prefix : <https://dj1tjoo.github.io/linked-data-supermarket#> .
@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix terms: <https://dj1tjoo.github.io/linked-data-supermarket/terms/> .

<https://dj1tjoo.github.io/linked-data-supermarket/> a owl:Ontology .

-----------
# Classes
-----------

:Product a owl:Class .
terms:Vegetable a owl:Class .

terms:Color a owl:Class .
terms:NutritionalValue a owl:Class .

terms:GrowingCondition a owl:Class .

terms:Soil a owl:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf terms:GrowingCondition .
terms:Climate a owl:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf terms:GrowingCondition .
terms:Sunlight a owl:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf terms:GrowingCondition .
terms:Watering a owl:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf terms:GrowingCondition .

terms:Season a owl:Class .
terms:Availability a owl:Class .
terms:StorageRequirement a owl:Class .

-----------
# Object Properties
-----------

terms:variantOf a owl:ObjectProperty .

terms:hasColor a owl:ObjectProperty .
terms:hasNutritionalValue a owl:ObjectProperty .
terms:hasLossRate a owl:ObjectProperty .

terms:growingCondition a owl:ObjectProperty .
terms:growsIn a owl:ObjectProperty

terms:availableIn a owl:ObjectProperty .

terms:storedLike a owl:ObjectProperty .

-----------
# Datatype Properties
-----------

terms:name a owl:DatatypeProperty .

terms:scientificName a owl:DatatypeProperty .
terms:origin a owl:DatatypeProperty .
terms:shelfLife a owl:DatatypeProperty .
terms:healthBenefits a owl:DatatypeProperty .
terms:commonVariety a owl:DatatypeProperty .

terms:kcal a owl:DatatypeProperty .
terms:protein a owl:DatatypeProperty .
terms:fiber a owl:DatatypeProperty .